<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <style>
    @media only screen and (max-width: 480px) {
      .content-pad { padding: 16px !important; }
      .header-pad { padding: 16px !important; }
      .info-table td { display: block !important; width: 100% !important; padding: 3px 0 !important; }
      .info-table td:first-child { padding-bottom: 0 !important; }
      .status-box { display: block !important; margin: 8px 0 !important; }
      .status-arrow { display: block !important; margin: 8px 0 !important; font-size: 16px !important; }
      .badge { font-size: 10px !important; padding: 2px 8px !important; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f4f4f4;">
  <table style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #fff;" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
    <tr>
      <td class="header-pad" style="background: #2563eb; padding: 24px; text-align: center;">
        <h1 style="color: #fff; margin: 0; font-size: 18px;">Cập nhật trạng thái đơn hàng</h1>
      </td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td class="content-pad" style="padding: 24px;">
        <p style="font-size: 14px; color: #333; margin: 0 0 4px;">Xin chào <strong><%= full_name %></strong>,</p>
        <p style="font-size: 13px; color: #555; margin: 0 0 16px;">Đơn hàng <strong>#<%= order.id %></strong> đã được cập nhật trạng thái.</p>

        <table style="width: 100%; background: #f9fafb; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 12px 0; text-align: center; border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
          <tr>
            <td align="center">
              <table style="margin: 0 auto;" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                <tr>
                  <td class="status-box" style="display: inline-block; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; background: #f1f5f9; color: #64748b; white-space: nowrap;">
                    <%= old_status_label %>
                  </td>
                  <td class="status-arrow" style="display: inline-block; padding: 0 10px; font-size: 18px; color: #3b82f6; vertical-align: middle;">→</td>
                  <td class="status-box" style="display: inline-block; padding: 6px 14px; border-radius: 6px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: bold; background: #dbeafe; color: #1d4ed8; white-space: nowrap;">
                    <%= new_status_label %>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>

        <table class="info-table" style="width: 100%; background: #f9fafb; border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px; font-size: 13px; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 12px 0;">
          <tr><td style="padding: 3px 0; color: #64748b; width: 40%;">Số hóa đơn</td><td style="padding: 3px 0; color: #333; font-weight: bold;">#<%= order.id %></td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding: 3px 0; color: #64748b;">Khách hàng</td><td style="padding: 3px 0; color: #333;"><%= full_name %></td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding: 3px 0; color: #64748b;">Email</td><td style="padding: 3px 0; color: #333;"><%= order.user_email %></td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding: 3px 0; color: #64748b;">Ngày đặt</td><td style="padding: 3px 0; color: #333;"><%= order.created_at ? new Date(order.created_at).toLocaleString('vi-VN') : '---' %></td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding: 3px 0; color: #64748b;">Cập nhật lúc</td><td style="padding: 3px 0; color: #333;"><%= new Date().toLocaleString('vi-VN') %></td></tr>
          <tr><td style="padding: 3px 0; color: #64748b;">Thanh toán</td><td style="padding: 3px 0; color: #333;"><%= payment_method %></td></tr>
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 3px 0; color: #64748b;">TT thanh toán</td>
            <td style="padding: 3px 0;">
              <span class="badge" style="display: inline-block; padding: 2px 10px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 11px; font-weight: bold; background: <%= payment_status === 'Paid' ? '#dcfce7' : '#fef3c7' %>; color: <%= payment_status === 'Paid' ? '#16a34a' : '#d97706' %>;"><%= payment_status_label %></span>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr><td style="padding: 3px 0; color: #64748b;">Tổng tiền</td><td style="padding: 3px 0; color: #dc2626; font-weight: bold;"><%= formatPrice(order.final_amount) %></td></tr>
        </table>

        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #888; margin-top: 20px; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid #e2e8f0;">
          Nếu có thắc mắc, vui lòng trả lời email này hoặc liên hệ với chúng tôi.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #888;">Trân trọng,<br><strong>Sport Nexus</strong></p>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
